{"tid":955025,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【連燈仔越反，喜茶就越強大】喜茶沙田分店繼續墟冚 學生晨早排隊3小時","createTime":"2018-12-25T05:47:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-25T06:37:32.000Z","uid":37358,"like":4,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1bbf2a4377622a215306839e5d2e6973debc2399","tid":955025,"uid":37358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T05:47:17.000Z","msg":"內地品茶店「喜茶HEYTEA」平安夜（24日）於香港開設首間分店，首3日更設買一送一優惠，吸引逾300人於店外排隊等候。該店今日繼續實施限購，每人只限購買一單，即2杯飲品，而每單只會贈送1杯飲品，開店前已吸引大班年輕人到場輪候，有排隊顧客表示早在開店3個小時前已到達。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》今早約9時半到達喜茶位於沙田新城市廣場的分店，發現現場已有逾百人排隊，人龍「打蛇餅」佔據商場半層位置。排第二位的中四學生劉同學稱，今早7時多已到達店外，自己是看到朋友在社交媒體的帖文，受喜茶門面裝修等吸引前來，「都係想打下卡」。被問到家人對她假日一早出門有何反應，她指媽媽沒有阻止她出門，還叫她幫忙買一杯。直至下午一時許，喜茶門外排隊的人龍有增無減，佔據商場大半層。<br />\n<br />\n冠域商業及經濟研究中心主任關焯照指，店舖短時間內吸引長長的排隊人龍，的確會對其他消費者造成心理影響，吸引顧客「人排你又排」，加上近日有節日效應，料人潮會持續。不過，排隊人龍同時會提高顧客預期，「無條龍你預期無咁高，如果飲完覺得唔係咁好，就以後都唔會返轉頭，等於上釣一次就唔會再上釣。」<br />\n<br />\n他認為，茶飲店中長期能否維持生意要視乎質素，因品牌效應亦會褪色。現時茶飲店入場門檻不高，越開越多，但人的口味隨時變化，隨時就不再流行，「同埋已經行咗咁耐，係咁濫開會分薄盈利；小心個光輝一完就全部冧晒。」他續指，除非茶飲店有獨門秘方，否則未必能長期維持生意，「好彩就2、3年，唔好彩1年啲熱潮就無晒。」  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181225/59068226?fbclid=IwAR2aNWpsPpLqqOOQUcRlbU74kXN-6VzVCuupyrW4G9jTp37giP00muz1PT8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181225%2F59068226%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2aNWpsPpLqqOOQUcRlbU74kXN-6VzVCuupyrW4G9jTp37giP00muz1PT8&d=alT2BSZizqkq1jNfek8TezANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=e0c1a397\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181225%2F59068226%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2aNWpsPpLqqOOQUcRlbU74kXN-6VzVCuupyrW4G9jTp37giP00muz1PT8&h=525a45a2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181225/59068226?fbclid=IwAR2aNWpsPpLqqOOQUcRlbU74kXN-6VzVCuupyrW4G9jTp37giP00muz1PT8</a><br />\n<br />\n喜茶 2：0 連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce8eb50947561ed5a1a58d8ce3a4bd0c3a306666","tid":955025,"uid":94828,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T05:51:36.000Z","msg":"等睇全部中毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33db7bac02da67da80a4d17df74c06481e38a776","tid":955025,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T05:51:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74cd129d59312fffc93f79feeea2f0a143080c5f","tid":955025,"uid":18350,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T05:59:10.000Z","msg":"排超過十五分鐘買杯野飲既智力一定有問題<br />\n不論幸福堂定喜茶定乜鳩"},{"pid":"5a64b9121441a4bb967cb51e67808f425aa8782a","tid":955025,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T06:10:17.000Z","msg":"請人排隊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb9cfa01ba9fb39210e8fd00352133e7901bd781","tid":955025,"uid":150609,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T06:15:58.000Z","msg":"d人咁有錢  30幾40蚊一杯野- -"},{"pid":"86207e29c6ae120f1a61d1c0bacf4398ec527776","tid":955025,"uid":12994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T06:21:38.000Z","msg":"有無諗過其實係沙田多大陸仔同新移民😂"},{"pid":"eef5a5c433c2539d8c75785090bd421dacec540a","tid":955025,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb9cfa01ba9fb39210e8fd00352133e7901bd781","tid":955025,"uid":150609,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T06:15:58.000Z","msg":"d人咁有錢  30幾40蚊一杯野- -"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T06:33:36.000Z","msg":"買個中產/文青feel+打卡,對佢地黎講係值得<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3de85a9b913b72b3d37cde51315a43ca53a368e","tid":955025,"uid":59041,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T06:35:31.000Z","msg":"識做生意既一定要睇連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif